snippet.title: Knockout City Season 7: Mutant Mutiny! Brawl Pass Trailer
snippet.description:
The Mutants have a massive deal for you! Ratfink makes the pitch for The Mutants’ very own Brawl Pass filled with unlockable cosmetics and an epic new story to accompany Knockout City’s seventh Season, Mutant Mutiny. If you want Outfits that are oozy on the eyes, then don’t change that channel!

Can't get enough of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles? Then level up your Brawl Pass! Earn April O’Neil’s Channel 6 Jumpsuit, Shredder's Mask, and other radical TMNT-themed rewards. Earn a slew of items by leveling up through Brawl Pass Contracts, with a Free and Premium Tier available. Get ready to be wowed!
